### What To Keep Exactly As-Is

- All of `vis.js` graph rendering
- `bindings.js` — click/keypress handling works perfectly
- `network_serialize.js` — share-by-URL feature is a great free feature to keep
- `commafield.js` — multi-topic input is useful for Fractal too
